  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink29-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> varaivetir koḷḷār tamar avaṇ maṟuppuḻit tōḻi cevilikku aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink29">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> māri kaṭikoḷak kāvalar kaṭuka</l>
          <l> vittiya veṇmuḷai kaḷva ṉaṟukkuṅ</l>
          <l> kaḻaṉi yūraṉ mārpuṟa marīit</l>
          <l> titalai yalku ṉiṉmakaḷ</l>
          <l> pacalai koḷva tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> After she united with and possessed the chest of the man from the village of paddy
            fields where </l>
          <l rend='indent2'> when the watchmen hasten to find protection from showers</l>
          <l> the crab tears off the white sprouts that have been sown–</l>
          <l> What is this pallor taking your daughter</l>
          <l> of the beauty-spotted hips, mother?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
